thread.title: James & Rachael
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by James & Rachael

author: James & Rachael
title: James & Rachael
text: We recently sold our property in Kensington with the help of Nelson Alexander, and were very happy with the way they handled everything. Jayson and his team (Kate and Josh) were all very pleasant and professional. They assisted before the campaign started to ensure house was ready by promptly providing contacts for cleaning and painting etc, and the campaign was then quite seamless, and we were informed thoroughly about outcomes of viewings and potential buyers. The auction day itself went very smoothly and achieved a great result. I would highly recommend Jayson and the team at Nelson Alexander Flemington.
